Description:
THE COMPLETE PACKAGE
CRANBOURNE EAST: With extraordinary attention to detail, no expense has been spared in the construction of this one of a kind family home. Ideally suited to both first timers and down sizers, this functional floor plan would also suit those who are looking to invest.
This magnificent property is situated in an established street location within the prestigious Parks Edge Estate. It is simply a case of moving in, unpacking and enjoying a luxurious lifestyle.
The master bedroom offers a full en suite with walk in robe. There is plenty of space in the master bedroom for you to have your own dressing table or TV stand. All the other bedrooms have double door built in robes and they are located at a distance from the master bed room. The spacious and separate bathroom is set up close to the other bedrooms.
Anyone who enjoys an open plan structure will surely fall in love with the makeup of the kitchen, study area, open plan living and the outdoor access to the alfresco area with decking. This gem of a house offers fully secure and landscaped gardens as well.
Summary of internal and external features include:
- Built in 2013
- Approx. 400sqm land
- Study area with built in desk
- Porcelain tiles
- High ceiling
- Glass Splash Back
- Caesar stone bench top in Kitchen
- 900 mm stainless steel oven
- 900 mm cook top
- Large fridge space
- Microwave cavity
- Built in Pantry
- Dishwasher
- Overhead cupboards in the kitchen
- Stainless steel range hood
- Ducted heating
- Solar power electricity
- Remote controlled double lock up garage
- Internal access
- Overhead cupboards in the laundry
- Sliding doors in to Alfresco
- Alfresco and Decking area
- Fully landscaped garden
- Fully secure backyard
* The location of this quality home is second to none with all the major amenities on your door step. Your family can enjoy the open space for many years to come.
This property is situated within close proximity to Cranbourne East Primary and Cranbourne East Secondary College, as well as Cranbourne Secondary College and is surrounded by multiple Shopping Centres. Also located nearby, is the newly constructed Casey Fields football ground, Casey Race Recreation & Aquatic Centre and Casey Library.

Description:
LOW MAINTENANCE LIVING!
Cranbourne East - Set in the heart of the Hunt Club estate surrounded by quality built and well presented homes, this home would suit an investor, a first home buyer or someone looking to down size.
As you enter you are greeted with a wide entrance leading into the large master bedroom with double doors, full ensuite and walk in robe. The hallway leads down to bedrooms 2 and 3 and the functional bathroom. Offering a large light and bright kitchen overlooking the meals area and lounge room and large secure yard with established gardens for you to enjoy and colour bond fencing. Within walking distance to parklands, lakes and public transport, you will love the lifestyle that comes with this home!
Open plan living offering an abundance of natural light and functional living space. Kitchen with island bench, gas cooking, electric oven and dishwasher overlooks the meals area and lounge room. Outside you are greeted with a concrete area perfect for a summer BBQ or for the kids to ride their bikes and play and a safe and secure yard.
Features include:
- single lock up garage
- blend of tiles and carpet
- gas wall furnace
- colour bond fencing
- down lights
- double gate access to the yard
The Hunt Club is a multi award winning estate offering numerous parks, wetlands, walking and bicycle paths as well as a complete range of childcare, primary (Cranbourne East Primary) and secondary schools (Cranbourne East Secondary College). Buses weave through the estate making the newly built shopping centre complete with Woolworths & Aldi easily accessible. Recycled water, high speed broadband and environmentally friendly designs are all part of the estate.
At Ray White Cranbourne our price indications are based upon probable market value, the likely selling price and vendor expectations. You can view with confidence that vendors will sell within the range with favourable conditions.

Proudly positioned in a perfect location in Cranbourne East is this magnificent fully appointed family home. Description:
**SOLD BY MATTHEW RINGERI**
HUNT CLUB ESTATE, CRANBOURNE EAST (124726994): In what was the first of many estates creating the Cranbourne East we know today, this home is set in the heart of the highly sought after, award winning Hunt Club estate within a very quiet court like setting only moments away from all local amenities.
Ideal as a first home or a portfolio building investment, 2 Gallop Close is designed for low maintenance living which perfectly suits today's busy lifestyles. On a compact cottage block the home features a central hallway, open plan lounge/dining room with a gas heater plus a galley style kitchen complete with wall oven, gas cook top and a handy breakfast bar.
Don't forget the 3 robed bedrooms, including the master with a walk-in wardrobe and ensuite style access to the dual entry bathroom with separate powder room.
Outside you find a single garage with remote door and internal access as well as an easy care backyard with a covered patio that is great for relaxing and entertaining with family and friends.
Within close proximity to picturesque wetlands and walking/bike paths the Hunt Club is a multi-award winning estate offering a complete range of education facilities including a childcare centre, Cranbourne East Primary and Cranbourne East Secondary College. Buses weave through the estate whilst the recently opened Hunt Club Village has an array of shopping options. There are future plans for a Cranbourne East railway station as well. High speed broadband and environmentally friendly designs add to the overall appeal of this family orientated location!
The position is second to none! Centrally located to freeways and public transport enroute to the Melbourne CBD which is only app. 40 minutes away. For those of you who like to stay closer to home its only a brisk drive to Cranbourne Park Shopping Centre, Berwick Village, Fountain Gate Shopping Centre, Casey Lifestyle Centre and Casey Fields Sporting Complex. Within close vicinity to an array of further Primary, Secondary and Tertiary Institutions, the entire family has easy access to the very best in entertainment, education and recreation!

Description:
A Wealth Of Warmth In A Family Friendly Home
This beautifully presented three year old home set on a 548 m2 allotment in Cranbourne East has everything. Size and a truly versatile floor plan for the growing family. Located within walking distance to local schools, child care, gyms and the new Selandra Rise shopping centre, there are not many homes that could beat this location.
This beautiful family home consists of 4 large bedrooms, master with full ensuite and WIR, whilst remaining bedrooms have generous built in robes. The property has a natural flow in the layout which offers a fantastic open plan family living/meals area which is overlooked by a large kitchen with plenty of cupboard and bench space. The kitchen is sure to impress the fussiest of chefs, offering quality stainless steel appliances, walk in pantry, dishwasher and glass splash back. Modern study with lots of built in storage space. Double lock of garage with internal and rear access perfect for additional parking.
At the front of the house is an additional room with a separate kitchen offering great versatility for a home run business or the professional in mind.Outdoors is just as impressive with low maintenance large backyard. Other extras in the property include; ducted heating, evaporative cooling, down lights, 3.7kw solar panels ,ducted vacuum ready, fibre optic cable ready , solar hot water, additional power points and water taps around the house , quality fittings plus much more.
This is an opportunity not to be missed!
For inspections contact Leon D'Penha on 0415 205 032 today !

Description:
UNDER CONTRACT/ UNDER OFFER!
CRANBOURNE EAST: This fine family home allows the lucky new purchaser to move into the ever popular Hunt Club Estate.
This quality built home featuring 4 spacious bedrooms, the master suite is complete with a WIR and a FES, whilst bedrooms 2, 3 and 4 all have built in robes and are near to the family bathroom with separate bath and shower facilities!
The hostess kitchen is the central hub of the home and offers ample cupboard space, a wide fridge cavity, descent bench space, splash back and pantry. Stainless steel appliances including 900mm free standing oven/cooktop, dishwasher and rangehood.
With 2 spacious living zones and dining area you will have no issues being short on space or entertaining year in year out, with the added bonus of sliding door access out to the under roof alfresco perfect for all year-round use! Added internal extras freshly painted, gas ducted heating, split system cooling, combination of both carpet and tiles throughout the home, blinds and LED lighting.
Step outside and be greeted with a block measuring app. 506m2. The spacious rear yard offers an abundance of room for those with kids and pets, while the front yard is nicely manicured and low maintenance which adds to the overall street appeal, completed with remote DLUG with internal access.
The Hunt Club is a multi award winning estate offering numerous parks, wetlands, walking and bicycle paths as well as a complete range of childcare, primary (Cranbourne East Primary) and secondary schools (Cranbourne East Secondary College). Buses weave through the estate making the newly built shopping centre complete with Woolworths & Aldi easily accessible. Environmentally friendly designs are all part of the estate.

Description:
SOLD BY BRANDON WHITTA!
Cranbourne East: Located in the prestigious and tightly held Cascades on Clyde estate sits this astonishing 4 bedrooms plus study delight! boasting an enormous 600m2 block, this home ticks all the boxes and more!
Upon entry you will be immediately impressed by the quality on display, with a keen eye for detail this home will be sure to surprise even the pickiest of buyers. The huge master comes complete with his and hers walk in robes, massive full en suite with dual vanities and walk in shower space.
The hostess kitchen is a chef's dream and is complete with quality stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher, 900mm range hood, 5-burner gas cook top, caesar stone bench tops, glass splash back, ample overhead storage and bench space, dual ovens. Not to mention your very own butlers pantry fitted with an abundance of shelf space. All of this overlooking your separate meals and living zone.
Not only is this home fitted out with top quality fixtures and fittings it also presents a grand capacity to accommodate even the largest of families, this is truly an entertainers delight with multiple living zones on offer including an enormous enclosed theatre!
Added features include: down lights throughout, 3.5 kilowatt solar panel system, 2 separate powder rooms, Caesar stone bench tops in all bathrooms, laundry and powder rooms, ducted heating, evaporative cooling, exposed aggregate driveway, storage room in garage, walk in robes in all guest bedrooms and much more!
The additions dont stop there, step through the sliding door and enjoy your massive back yard, completely landscaped with decking, not to mention side access with plenty of room for caravans or boats!
Surrounded by top end properties and is within walking distance to picturesque wetlands, this home boasts convenience. Other estate features include Class- A recycled water ensuring lush gardens year round, over 14 hectares of parkland and public open space, public BBQ facilities, playgrounds and walking tracks.
Those who are business savvy will appreciate this Telstra smart community positioned within a short drive to all amenities located in the townships of Berwick, Clyde and Cranbourne. Minutes away from freeway access enroute to the Melbourne CBD, the popular Clyde Primary School, the recently constructed Casey Fields football ground/Casey Race aquatic centre and the Town Centre. Not to mention just seconds away from the newly developed Selanda rise and hunt Club village shopping centres.
From front to back this home was completed with an exceptional eye for detail and will be the perfect residence for those that expect nothing but the best!

Description:
Wow, I Want This One Darling!
## Mayfield Estate ## Built to Perfection. This home has everything you need. Whether you're a first home buyer, astute investor or downsizing, do not miss this perfect opportunity to own a prime piece of real estate in one of Australia's fastest growing suburbs, Cranbourne East!
Situated on a 463m2 block this home has been built with every creature comfort in mind, whether it be entertaining indoors or out, your covered. Offering a master bedroom (conveniently positioned at the rear of the house) with walk in robe and ensuite, a further 2 spacious bedrooms with built in robes, laundry, bathroom, separate toilet, open plan kitchen and enormous living and dining area. Other features include a covered alfresco area within inbuilt BBQ and exhaust fan perfect for all weather entertaining, low maintenance garden and double lock up garage, plus further concreted parking spot at the front of the house perfect for a boat, trailer or caravan. The kitchen itself is equipped with quality stainless steel products, including a 900mm built in oven and separate cook top, 40mm Caesar stone bench tops and plenty of cupboard space to cater for all your master chef needs!
Designed with luxury in mind, other features include;
* An array of quality pendant lights and down lights throughout
* Ducted heating
* Split system
* Evaporative cooling
* Supreme quality blinds
* Quality fixtures and fittings
* Landscaping to the front and rear yard
Enquire now and secure your dream home today!

Description:
EXCEPTIONAL FAMILY HOME IN CASCADES ON CLYDE!
Cranbourne East: Located in the prestigious and tightly held Cascades on Clyde estate sits this astonishing 4 bedrooms delight! boasting a massive 574m2 block, this home ticks all the boxes and more!
A top tier home in a top tier estate, with an array of separate living zones, elegant outdoor entertaining area with pergola and alfresco this exquisite residence is sure to suit even the most pickiest of buyers.
The generous sized master comes complete with walk in robes and a full ensuite which includes dual vanities and double headed shower space, while 2 guest bedrooms come fitted with built in robes of their own plus the remaining bedroom has the additional convenience of being fitted with a walk in robe!
The hostess kitchen is a chef's dream and is complete with quality stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher, 900mm range hood, 5-burner gas cook top, caesar stone bench tops, glass splash back, ample overhead storage/ bench space and walk in pantry. All of this overlooking your separate meals zone!
Added features include ducted heating and evaporative cooling, down lights throughout, rear access, internal access to your double lock up garage and much more!
If you love to entertain family and guests of all sizes you will have no issue providing the necessary amount of space, with a huge rumpus, separate living zone and general living area everyone will be accommodated for.
Step outside and enjoy your quality built large scale pergola and alfresco area, with a convenient blend of grass and pavement area both kids and parents will be able to enjoy their backyard to the fullest!
Those who are business savvy will appreciate this Telstra smart community positioned within a short drive to all amenities located in the townships of Berwick, Clyde and Cranbourne. Minutes away from freeway access enroute to the Melbourne CBD, the popular Clyde Primary School, the recently constructed Casey Fields football ground/Casey Race aquatic centre and the Town Centre. Not to mention just seconds away from the newly developed Selanda rise and hunt Club village shopping centres.
From front to back this home was completed with an exceptional eye for detail and will be the perfect residence for those that expect nothing but the best!

Description:
REAR ACCESS - PERFECT FAMILY HOME!
When you walk into this light home, you feel right at ease. This home boasts 3 good sized bedrooms with the master having a lovely bay window, walk in robe and ensuite. The master also has a ceiling fan to cool you down on those hot summer nights. The other two rooms both have built in wardrobes.
The family living and dining area consists of a split system cooler and ceiling fans as well, with newly laid floating floor boards. The kitchen is tiled with gas cook top and electric wall oven offering ample bench and cupboard space.
Outside has a huge under cover concreted pergola area leading from the back of the garage, which has rear roller door access perfect for access for cars, boats or caravans. There is still a sizable yard for the kids and animals to play on the grass!
Extras include:
- ducted heating,
- double remote garage with internal access,
- garden shed and so much more.
Cranbourne East is located on the outskirts of Cranbourne Central. The area offers Cranbourne East Primary and Cranbourne East Secondary College as well as Cranbourne Secondary College and is surrounded by multiple Shopping Centres. Also located nearby is the newly constructed Casey Fields football ground, Casey Race Recreation & Aquatic Centre, and Casey Library.
At Ray White Cranbourne our price indications are based upon probable market value, the likely selling price and vendor expectations. You can view with confidence that vendors will sell within the range with favourable conditions.
